How to add and use a class library
1. first you will have a basic solution, in that you will have a project so now you want to add a class library to it and use it
2. right click on the main solution and now you need to click on add project and add a class library this will create a dll.
3. suppose the code in the library is like below

namespace ClassLibrary1
{
    public class Class1
    {
        public int Add()
        {
            return 4;
        }
    }
}

class library that gets created is in the form of a dll

so now in main solution you have two project one is dll and one is the actual project
now go to the actual project and go to references and add the project references and now you should   be good.